#: /AB_CableMod/PowerGates/ProxSwitch/Build_AB-ProxSwitch.Default__Build_AB-ProxSwitch_C.mDescription
msgid ",A0E2B28E44B07FC59B4FC8BA4FFD2788"
msgstr "When an object is sensed infront of the panel the switch is engaged. It will stay on while anything is present. When empty, after a delay, the switch will turn off.\r\n\r\nKeep only the lights near you on, detect when vehicles are approaching crossings, or wait till you're nearby to run hypertube entrances.\r\n\r\nNote: Has been known to optimize itself into not toggling untill player is in general vicinty regardless of settings."

